  <trk>
    <name>Tour du Val d’Hérens: Grande Dixence – Arolla (Stage 2)</name>
    <desc>The second stage of the Tour du Val d&apos;Hérens leads from the world&apos;s highest gravity dam and along the longest reservoir in Switzerland to the foot of glacier-covered peaks. You will also discover a legendary mountain pass.</desc>
